stories.title: Five-wicket Franklin frazzles England
stories.subTitle: England v NZ, NatWest Series, Chester-le-Street
stories.summary: England picked up their dismal one-day form from where they had left off against West Indies at Trent Bridge, as New Zealand completed a thumping seven-wicket victory with exactly half of the day's left unused
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by Andrew Miller
